                            </p>
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            <p>
                                Your joining date with IndiaFirst will be on <span t-esc="o.date_joining" style="color: red; font-weight: bold;"/> (Expected date of joining,
                                provision to change the Date of joining). Please contact us immediately if you require
                                an alternative joining date. If you do not confirm your acceptance or we are unable to
                                set an alternative date, this offer will be withdrawn.
                            </p>
